Class FIXParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.custom.informatica.fab.credittrading.fix.FIXParser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    quickfix.Application

    public class FIXParser
extends java.lang.Object
implements quickfix.Application
    FIX Parser implementation using quickfixj 2.2.0 All properties are picked from property files. The initiator.cfg or initiator_bgc.config is used for all configuration relating to FIX
